OriginalText:

full_text: A reflection: Q1 2020 was a stressful period. As someone who lived in Asia & Australia, I kept uptodate with news of the emerging SARSCoV2 virus and pandemic. I forewarned my patients, friends and family since Jan 2020. Some accused me of scaremongering. 1/
OriginalText:
